# AI Operating Kit — .gitignore
#
# The public kit is intentionally generic. This file helps keep company-specific
# adaptations, real data, and filled-in templates OUT of a public repo.
# In your PRIVATE fork you may choose to remove some of these rules.

# --- Private, company-specific, or real-data files -------------------------
# Anything you tag as private stays untracked.
*-private.md
*.private.md
/_private/
/private/
/confidential/

# Filled-in working copies of templates (keep the blank templates, ignore real ones)
*-filled.md
*.filled.md
/_working/

# Real data exports, financials, forecasts, ledgers with actual numbers
*.csv
*.xlsx
*.xls
*.numbers
/exports/
/data/

# --- Secrets & credentials (never commit) ----------------------------------
.env
.env.*
*.key
*.pem
*.pfx
credentials*.json
secrets*.json
*-secrets.*

# --- Script backups created by install.sh ----------------------------------
CLAUDE.md.bak.*
*.bak
*.bak.*

# --- OS / editor cruft -----------------------------------------------------
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*.swo
*~
